===Etymology===
Borrowed in 1816 from {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|sémaphore|lang=fr}}, coined in French from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|σῆμα||sign|tr=sêma|lang=grc}}, and {{term||-φωρος|tr=-phoros|bearing, bearer|lang=grc}}, from {{term|φέρω||to bear, carry|tr=férō|lang=grc}}.

